<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>New Recovery Codes - Experience Enablers</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/style.css">
    <style>
        /* Use same base styles as other pages */
        .login-container {
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .login-box {
            background: white;
            padding: 40px;
            border-radius: 15px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            border: 3px solid #f3eb2e;
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 600px;
        }

        .login-logo {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }

        .login-logo img {
            max-width: 200px;
        }

        .warning-box {
            background: #fff3cd;
            border: 2px solid #ffeeba;
            color: #856404;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .warning-box h2 {
            color: #856404;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }

        .code-container {
            background: #f8f9fa;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }

        .code-box {
            background: white;
            border: 2px solid #643c94;
            padding: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }

        .code-box h3 {
            color: #643c94;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .code {
            font-family: monospace;
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            color: #212529;
            background: #e9ecef;
            padding: 10px;
            border-radius: 3px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .print-btn {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 15px;
            background: #643c94;
            color: white;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: background 0.3s ease;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }

        .print-btn:hover {
            background: #4a2d6f;
        }

        .continue-btn {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 15px;
            background: #28a745;
            color: white;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: background 0.3s ease;
            text-decoration: none;
            display: inline-block;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .continue-btn:hover {
            background: #218838;
        }

        @media print {
            .no-print {
                display: none;
            }

            .code-container {
                border: 1px solid #000;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="login-container">
        <div class="login-box">
            <div class="login-logo no-print">
                <img src="/images/nav_logo.png" alt="Experience Enablers Logo">
            </div>

            <div class="warning-box">
                <h2>⚠️ IMPORTANT ⚠️</h2>
                <p>Store these recovery codes in a secure location. They will not be shown again.</p>
                <p>You will need these codes if you forget your password.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="code-container">
                <div class="code-box">
                    <h3>Recovery Code 1 (Store in company safe)</h3>
                    <div class="code"><%= recoveryCode1 %></div>
                </div>

                <div class="code-box">
                    <h3>Recovery Code 2 (Store in secondary location)</h3>
                    <div class="code"><%= recoveryCode2 %></div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <button onclick="window.print()" class="print-btn no-print">
                Print Recovery Codes
            </button>

            <a href="/admin" class="continue-btn no-print">
                Continue to Admin Dashboard
            </a>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>